{"title_page": "This City (Sam Fischer song)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = This City\n| cover      = This City by Sam Fischer.png\n| alt        =\n| border     = yes\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Sam Fischer]]\n| EP         = Not a Hobby\n| released   = 18 January 2018\n| format     =\n*[[Music download|Digital download]]\n*[[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   = 2017\n| studio     =\n| genre      = \n| length     = 3:14\n| label      =\n*[[RCA Records|RCA]]\n*[[Sony Music Entertainment|Sony]]\n| writer     =\n* Sam Fischer\n* Jackson Morgan\n* [[James Michael Robbins]]\n| producer   = Sam Fischer\n| prev_title = Smoke\n| prev_year  = 2018\n| next_title = Restless\n| next_year  = 2018\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n| artist     = [[Sam Fischer]]\n| type       = singles\n| prev_title = Everybody Wants You\n| prev_year  = 2019\n| title = This City\n| year = 2019\n| next_title = \n| next_year  = }}\n{{External music video|{{YouTube|s3IAHXP1dfs|\"This City\"}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''This City'''\" is a song by Australian recording artist [[Sam Fischer]]. The song was recorded in 2017 and was released in January 2018 as the third and final single on Fischer's debut EP ''Not a Hobby''.<ref name=\"amazon18\">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/This-City/dp/B0792P43S3|title=This City single by Sam Fischer|website=Amazon|date=18 January 2018|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"HDD\"/> Fisher said \"I wrote this with [[James Michael Robbins]] and Jackson Morgan on a day when I felt pretty damn defeated by [[Los Angeles|LA]]. Change is really hard, but so important. This is my experience, one that almost everyone goes through, hope it helps in some way.\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/samfischermusic/videos/this-city-is-out-everywhere-but-spotify-right-now-but-were-working-on-it-%EF%B8%8F%EF%B8%8Fi-wro/1535664703136839/|title=\"This City\" Is Out|website=[[Facebook]]|date=18 January 2018|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref> \n\nAfter signing with [[RCA Records]] in 2019, the song was re-released.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sportplaylists.com/sam-fischer-this-city |title= Australian singer-songwriter Sam Fischer drops 'This City' single |date=20 December 2019 |accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"iTunes\"/> \n\n==Background and composition==\nFischer wrote \"This City\" in 2016 and it was released in early 2018 where it was shared by people including [[Meghan Trainor]] and [[Lewis Capaldi]].<ref name=\"TMN\"/> In 2020 Fischer reflects saying \"The song got a lot of eyes on it, but it wasn't getting any love from anyone for a long time except for the fans. When I say anyone, I mean [[Spotify]], [[Apple Music|Apple]], [[Amazon (company)|Amazon]]. But it was a fan-favourite.\"<ref name=\"TMN\"/>  \n\n18 months later, it was featured on [[TikTok]] and as Fischer says \"It changed everything for me\". The exposure lead to Fischer receiving a [[direct message|DM]] from [[RCA Records|RCA Records UK]] which lead to the signing.<ref name=\"TMN\">{{cite web|url=https://themusicnetwork.com/sam-fischer-interview/|title= Aussie hitmaker Sam Fischer talks isolation in LA & viral hit \"This City\"|website=The Music Network|date=25 March 2020 |accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"HDD\">{{cite web|url=https://hitsdailydouble.com/the_bside&id=319859|title=Sam Fischer (Sony U.K./RCA)|website=Hits Daily Double|date=2 April 2020|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Track listings==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Original<ref name=\"iTunes\"/>\n| title1  = This City\n| length1 = 3:14\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Luca Schreiner remix<ref name=\"Luca\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/this-city-luca-schreiner-remix-single/1495078031|title=This City Luca Schreiner remix- single |website=Apple Music|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| title1  = This City\n| note1   = [[Luca Schreiner]] remix\n| length1 = 2:56\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Acoustic<ref name=\"Acoustic\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/this-city-acoustic-single/1503376988|title=This City Acoustic- single |website=Apple Music|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| title1  = This City\n| note1   = Acoustic remix\n| length1 = 3:26\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Frank Walker remix<ref name=\"Frank\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/this-city-frank-walker-remix-single/1505596218|title=This City Frank Walker remix - single |website=Apple Music|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| title1  = This City\n| note1   = Frank Walker remix\n| length1 = 2:50\n}}\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n!scope=\"col\"| Peak<br>position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australian Artists ([[ARIA Charts]])<ref name=\"13Apr20\">{{cite web|url=http://cdn.aria.com.au/pdfs/2FCAB7CA836D3EDE9F269863D8D40B95F988E96FD99682B5262F650135DFB2B1/ARIA%20Australian%20Artist%20Singles%20Chart.pdf?seq=31|title=ARIA Australian Artist Singles Chart|publisher=[[ARIA]]|date=13 April 2020|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n{{single chart|Ireland4|41|date=20200417|rowheader=true|accessdate=18 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Scotland|50|date=20200410|rowheader=true|accessdate=11 April 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Singles ([[UK Singles Chart|Official Charts Company]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/57090/sam-fischer/|title=Sam Fischer {{!}} full Official Chart history|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 33\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Adult Top 40]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/adult-pop-songs/2020-04-18|title=Adult Pop Songs: April 18, 2020|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=14 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 24\n|}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n! Region\n! Date\n! Format\n! Label\n! Version\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| Various\n| 18 January 201